## Design Principles

- Flow dominates. Pulse assists. Authority empowers.
- Never sacrifice clarity for aesthetics.
- Never gamify at the expense of trust.
- Always prioritize insight over raw data display.
- Build systems, not features.
- Pulse elements only appear when backed by real data.
